1.17
log
@Remove SHA-0 support.

SHA-0 was withdrawn shortly after publication 20 years ago and replaced
with SHA-1.  This will require a major crank.

ok bcook@@, jsing@@
@
text
@/* $OpenBSD: m_sha.c,v 1.16 2014/07/13 09:30:02 miod Exp $ */
